##YOU WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND! "Male God" Zhang Wenhong said the big truth again

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

This is a roundup for the paper

This morning, the Shanghai Municipal Clinical Center for Public Health again came good news: 22 patients were discharged from hospital, including three critically ill patients. So far, the cure discharge rate has exceeded 74% .

When will the much-anticipated "Shanghai Plan" come out? According to Zhang Wenhong, head of the Shanghai Medical Treatment Expert Group and director of the Infection Department of Mount Hua Hospital, the Shanghai plan is not written on paper, but written on the patient. The treatment plan is written only on the patient, to think that this treatment is the right one. "So, these patients were discharged, and I think the Shanghai plan was put in place. "

At present, older patients in Shanghai are more likely to cause disease progression, which also poses a greater challenge to the medical team. So for the critically ill patients, critically ill patients treatment program, what are the characteristics of Shanghai?

Zhang Wenhong said in an interview with reporters that, "I'll tell you what you can't understand, because we read different books. You can understand every Chinese character I speak, but you won't know what it means. But there is one sentence you can understand. "

Then he used this sentence to sum up the characteristics of the treatment program for the critically ill patients in Shanghai: that is, under the unified coordination of the Shanghai Municipal Government and the health commission, all the advantages of the city's resources, multidisciplinary team all gathered here, together to cure.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
And just last night, Zhang Wenhong also served as a guest speaker at an event in Shanghai, sharing his book list with netizens to discuss how to live a normal life during the epidemic prevention and control. In nearly an hour of live time, Zhang Wenhong and burst out of what golden sentences? Here's what you need to know:

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Professor Cheung man-wang, chief of infection, Mount Hua Hospital. Deng Chaojiantu is a reporter for the paper


Fire, theft, co-workers

Shanghai has survived the 14-day mark, and most people have been tested and diagnosed with a precipitous drop in numbers.

He says people can get out and about slowly and in a controlled way, but with masks on. "You have to be alert, don't fool around, don't take off your mask, don't talk, don't eat together, don't cancel unnecessary activities. Normal life is slowly returning, but not to the point of doing whatever you want.

Zhang Wenhong suggested that we do a good job of self-protection, wear a mask, wash hands frequently.

At the same time he also stressed the previous brush screen "golden sentence" : "Fire and theft prevention colleagues. Earlier, it was reported that Zhang Wenhong, the "God of Banter, " had a golden phrase again


Watching Boring TV shows to relieve fatigue

In the current outbreak, many front-line medical workers are working more than 15 or 16 hours a day. When talking about how to rest, Zhang Wenhong revealed that surgeons go home in the middle of the night, home feeling is "Ge you lie. ".

He said, "It's as rare as Professor Zhong Nanshan's musculature. Exercise is great, and I love it, but it's exhausting, and I've bought a gym membership, and I go there two or three times a year, and once the gym closes. Exercise for me is a weekend walk, run, quiet rest."

In the extreme fatigue, Zhang Wenhong also love to see more "boring" soap opera, not too much brain, to relax themselves.


I know what it's like to be bullied

"reading is one of the best ways to relieve anxiety, " Zhang said, adding that he would like to read popular science books during this special period.

"There are people in society who feel like they are being bullied all the time, and I've been bullied my whole life, and now that I'm over 50, I understand a lot of people's feelings. Read a lot of books, you can understand the face of a bully, to bully your people you go around, unless you are strong. When you are bullied, you have to learn how to be more kind to others, empathize with others, put yourself in their shoes, and see things from a different perspective."

Since the outbreak of the COVID-19, Zhang Wenhong has become a trusted "hard core expert" on the Internet because of his frank and responsible remarks:

"Take everyone off and let the Communists go! " "You're not quarantined at home, you're fighting! You're bored, bored for two weeks, and the virus will be 'smothered' by you. " "Fire and theft prevention colleagues" and so on are all over the Internet, also let many people who are in a state of nervous panic feel relieved.
